{"tid":230862,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀緊CS既朋友可唔可以幫下我 :(","createTime":"2017-05-05T16:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T09:00:15.000Z","uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2f4c62ab01541fe221031b08250700592dfd06","tid":230862,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"我而家做緊一份assignment, 係要係一個迷宮入面搵到最短既走出路線.<br />\n咁我個迷宮就會係用一個txt file做input, 就好似圖入面咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2T38O4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2T38O4.png&h=ce643fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n'#' 係impossible wall<br />\n'.' 係open space<br />\n'S' 同 'F' 係start 同 finish<br />\n咁問題黎啦, 我知道點樣搵shorest path (用BFS algorithm), 但係我唔知黠樣將佢用adjacency list去儲存呢一個迷宮.<br />\n其實我知道淨係需要儲存佢所有既open space, start point 同 exit<br />\n我而家諗到一個方法就只係用dictionary去儲存佢既rows同columns number, 不過我tutor話我唔需要用到dictionary(inefficient).<br />\n有冇人可以幫幫我 :(<br />\n(我想講女仔真係唔應該讀CS)"},{"pid":"a1fb3fc394a4b7b0bd5516ff942f153f4e6c8132","tid":230862,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"講漏左: 我用緊python去做呢份assignment"},{"pid":"26c5fda80b44171f4395cadb4b4dd3d9f27de311","tid":230862,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"女仔讀CS都唔收返半打兵幫自己做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94722091fb676414ffcaa1d0a4101cbf642aefd7","tid":230862,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女仔讀CS都唔收返半打兵幫自己做功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇資格收兵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d07f269f54d5f4e06f7a0db32b94bfd1b9a643","tid":230862,"uid":76233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"Pushh"},{"pid":"ffaea6a9275284db2f8eda956da815b075ec296a","