 1<br />\n2  3<br />\nlist[4]:  list[0]={2}, list[1]={-1}, list[2]={0,3}, list[3]={2}<br />\n到時做既時候無視-1既node"},{"pid":"5049e270d78b938f20af220a49b5d74eb220811c","tid":230862,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/OceanYeungSH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FOceanYeungSH&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5ed890c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/OceanYeungSH</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa52c9f760707d328febdad225da771c69fb03a","tid":230862,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A* algorithm</blockquote><br />\n我一定要用BFS去做<br />\n但我唔係唔識搵shortest path呀<br />\n係唔識點樣store個迷宮<br />\n其實tutor就講話用adj list（唔係adj matrix)<br />\n但我唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nadjacent list咪迷宮有n個格，就開n個vector type既array represent咁多個格<br />\nvector 入面裝嗰格同邊條友相鄰<br />\n例如n=<span style=\"color: red;\">4</span><br />\n.  #<br />\n.  .<br />\n由其編個名<br />\n0  1<br />\n2  3<br />\nlist[4]:  list[0]={2}, list[1]={-1}, list[2]={0,3}, list[3]={2}<br />\n到時做既時候無視-1既node</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b5a6cc517dccdd6b195e6641a178a72c5bfb7b","tid":230862,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"java一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n找我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/OceanYeungSH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FOceanYeungSH&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5ed890c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/OceanYeungSH</a>"},{"pid":"d2ad4247dbaf508ad3d730434b89b81d78d01e76","tid":230862,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"char[] []  map =new char[i] [j];"},{"pid":"15f57235d5378a27edbb26b5aee1f368a9d97c75","tid":230862,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A* algorithm</blockquote><br />\n我一定要用BFS去做<br />\n但我唔係唔識搵shortest path呀<br />\n係唔識點樣store個迷宮<br />\n其實tutor就講話用adj list（唔係adj matrix)<br />\n但我唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nadjacent list咪迷宮有n個格，就開n個vector type既array represent咁多個格<br />\nvector 入面裝嗰格同邊條友相鄰<br />\n例如n=2<br />\n.  #<br />\n.  .<br />\n由其編個名<br />\n0  1<br />\n2  3<br />\nlist[4]:  list[0]={2}, list[1]={-1}, list[2]={0,3}, list[3]={2}<br />\n到時做既時候無視-1既node</blockquote><br />\n但你要將每一個格都俾個名佢，唔會浪費左啲memory?因為我地唔需要儲存#（impose wall)<br />\n同埋到時我個tutor interview 我個陣會要我run 500x500既maze<br />\n佢話正常最多幾秒就會run完<br />\n佢就用左0.667秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18a560d128a86c845ecdc970187089da9f48e1f","tid":230862,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Use a 48x48 adjacent matrix to represent a directed graph<br />\n<br />\nThat apply Dijkstra's algorithm<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53G3BV9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53G3BV9.jpg&h=348ecbb5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔可以用matrix 因為inefficient"},{"pid":"834643f6b0f9a23f3dc00244b5b21862f1d2539e","tid":230862,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T14:02:07.000Z","msg":"係python 世界點叫一個dictionary..<br />\n如果我用c 既諗法，呢條要起個struct 係最efficient.."},{"pid":"8cbff779021a29536e2a313b19a7a792a916b9e8","tid":230862,"uid":13020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A* algorithm</blockquote><br />\n我一定要用BFS去做<br />\n但我唔係唔識搵shortest path呀<br />\n係唔識點樣store個迷宮<br />\n其實tutor就講話用adj list（唔係adj matrix)<br />\n但我唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nadjacent list咪迷宮有n個格，就開n個vector type既array represent咁多個格<br />\nvector 入面裝嗰格同邊條友相鄰<br />\n例如n=2<br />\n.  #<br />\n.  .<br />\n由其編個名<br />\n0  1<br />\n2  3<br />\nlist[4]:  list[0]={2}, list[1]={-1}, list[2]={0,3}, list[3]={2}<br />\n到時做既時候無視-1既node</blockquote><br />\n但你要將每一個格都俾個名佢，唔會浪費左啲memory?因為我地唔需要儲存#（impose wall)<br />\n同埋到時我個tutor interview 我個陣會要我run 500x500既maze<br />\n佢話正常最多幾秒就會run完<br />\n佢就用左0.667秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYou can skip the wall when building the graph.<br />\nThe array-like map might confused you. Try imagine it is an unordered graph built with all the empty space only."}]}